a54221787","tid":177482,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:50:18.000Z","msg":"唔係講笑，我就快痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9342e37a997fa03f8add72e22bf0a819c888122a","tid":177482,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:42:48.000Z","msg":"終於lunch time，可以平靜少少。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fa2a14728cd1c8344bb442fe4f1492fb8398c1","tid":177482,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"救命個心又開始跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576f4d8ba2d9142984a0567b06018598a2d57f77","tid":177482,"uid":49912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>救命個心又開始跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一刻心也跳著<br />\n命能懸著<br />\n尚能延著"},{"pid":"90c6f24624a68a3ac5548d235693cebfe722fd1c","tid":177482,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>救命個心又開始跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一刻心也跳著<br />\n命能懸著<br />\n尚能延著</blockquote><br />\n個腦好攰，想訓，但個心係咁跳我訓唔到。<br />\n手又開始震了，又黎料了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcc760e7bb745cd38f219200f717aaf328d4de2","tid":177482,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"我控制唔到我自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前跳掣都係十零廿分鐘既事。<br />\n今朝跳左3個鐘，停左一陣間又跳過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29505c1407d09cc356c848b908193b36b03c0965","tid":177482,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>救命個心又開始跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n救命 我個心唔跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f012982db40eb0c2d3a092bf50013524662ed400","tid":177482,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>救命個心又開始跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n救命 我個心唔跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}